column16:
'desc': [u'

Chicco Cotton Buds Safe Hygiene (Pack of 64) Price: Rs.119

Cotton buds are used for various purposes ranging from applying and removing make-up to cleaning an infant's ear. The cotton swabs that used to clean a baby's ear has to be made of skin friendly fibers that do not irritate the delicate skin of the child. Chicco's Safe Hygiene Cotton Buds are made of the finest quality of cotton. This 100 per cent cotton fibers are treated to make sure that they are antibacterial. As these Cotton swabs have ear drum protection
column17:
you can safely use these Safe Hygiene Cotton buds to gently clean the ear canal. Always make sure that your tiny tot\'s do not use any cotton swab all by themselves. The Cotton Buds from Chicco are perfect for daily grooming and hygiene needs.
